data.description: WELCOME HOME!  This beautiful custom built (Vera Construction) home is nestled away in a quiet cul-de-sac in the desired subdivision of La Campana in Edcouch-Elsa. This beauty features an open floor plan with foyer opening up to an office with built-ins, a spacious kitchen with granite tops, stainless steel appliances that looks into the nook and living room, great for entertaining friends and loved ones for all occasions. French doors lead to a covered patio and a spacious backyard on a 0.71 acre lot that has ample room to create your very own oasis for entertainment and relaxation.  This 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathrooms offers a split bedroom concept, the primary features a connecting full bathroom that includes double vanity sinks and walk in closet. Extra storage - room to store your seasonal decor, can be used as a play room for the fur babies or whatever you may desire to store. The 2 car garage with an extended driveway can fit up to 6 vehicles.
